# Git and Production Deployment

- Push this repository through its dedicated SSH host alias:
  `git@github-devilxdetail:DevilxDetail/DxD-Web-v3-React.git`.
- Before pushing, verify `ssh -T git@github-devilxdetail` authenticates as
  `DevilxDetail`.
- Never use the default `github.com` SSH identity for this repository; it
  belongs to a different GitHub account used by other projects.
- Push production changes with `git push origin main`.
- Vercel deploys production automatically after `main` reaches GitHub.
- See `README.md` for the documented workflow.
